Preshower Simulation v0.1 for Geant4 

UTFSM - CCTVAL

----------------------------------------------------------------------

- Installing

To compile the program you need geant4, at least version 4.9.5 and cmake.
Default visualization program is opengl, can be change inside vis.mac

1. Inside Preshower code folder run:
   cd ..
   mkdir preshower-build
   cd preshower-build
   cmake -DGeant4_DIR=$GEANT4_DIR ../$PRESHOWER_FOLDER

2. Tu run the code. Inside preshower-build folder:
   make
   ./matrix



